    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Finding fossil man",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.59,
      "endTime": 10.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why are legends handed down by storytellers useful?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.9,
      "endTime": 17.42,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "We can read of things that happened 5, 000 years ago in the Near East,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 17.43,
      "endTime": 23.27,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "where people first learned to write.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.28,
      "endTime": 26.91
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But there are some parts of the world where even now people cannot write.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.92,
      "endTime": 33.39,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The only way that they can preserve their history is to recount it as sagas legends handed down from one generation of storytellers to another.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "endTime": 46.14,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "These legends are useful because they can tell us something about migrations of people who lived long ago,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.15,
      "endTime": 54.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but none could write down what they did.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 54.22,
      "endTime": 57.66,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Anthropologists wondered where the remote ancestors of the Polynesian peoples now living in the Pacific Islandscame from.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.67,
      "endTime": 66.9
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The sagas of these people explain that some of them came from Indonesia about 2, 000 years ago.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.91,
      "endTime": 75.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But the first people who were like ourselves lived so long ago that even their sagas, if they had any, are forgotten.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.26,
      "endTime": 85.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "So archaeologists have neither history nor legends to help them to find out where the first 'modern men' came from.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 85.71,
      "endTime": 94.83
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Fortunately, however, ancient men made tools of stone, especially flint,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.84,
      "endTime": 101.44
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "because this is easier to shape than other kinds.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.45,
      "endTime": 105.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They may also have used wood and skins, but these have rotted away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.74,
      "endTime": 112.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Stone does not decay, and so the tools of long ago have remained when even the bones of the men who made them have disappeared without trace.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.16,
      "endTime": 117.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
